scripts.start: rm -rf .parcel-cache && rm -rf watch && parcel public/index.html --dist-dir watch
scripts.starttsx: rm -rf .parcel-cache && rm -rf watch && parcel src/index.tsx --dist-dir watch
scripts.build: rm -rf .parcel-cache && rm -rf dist && parcel build public/index.html --public-url '.' --reporter @parcel/reporter-bundle-analyzer
scripts.buildtsx: rm -rf .parcel-cache && rm -rf dist && parcel build src/index.tsx --public-url '.' --reporter @parcel/reporter-bundle-analyzer
